name: 拳术——Fists
notes: Gains half of Rank EXP if the attack was avoided or parried

name: 强化风系——Augment Air
notes: If a matching Instill skill is equipped, it will also reduce Final Damage of incoming hits from the element it protects against by 4% per Rank of this skill

name: 格挡——Parry
notes: Gains Rank EXP on getting hit or parrying the attack, zero if it was avoided

name: 压制——Overpower
notes: Gains Rank EXP if the attack was successful or parried, zero if it was avoided

name: 壁垒光环V——Rampart Aura V
notes: Tier V is only available by using Broaden Force while having Tier IV equipped

name: 击退I——Bash I
notes: It is only possible to knock back units in the same size category or smaller

name: 功效I——Efficacy I
notes: This skill reduces the amount of spent MP, the original amount is still needed to cast the spell

name: 死者的哀歌——Lament Of The Dead
戈尔迪之结（难解之结）——Gordian Lock
埃尔科拉斯之风——El Colas Winds
弹道——Trajectory
notes: Mages can use this skill to show the trajectory of their innate ranged attack, projectile spells will mostly match it
